// Grammar for the consumer-lane smoke tests.
//
// Deliberately tiny.  This lane's job is the cross-module @fltk// load path
// (macro resolution, crate/pip hubs, generated-artifact import), not generator
// breadth: breadth is covered in-repo by
// fltk/fegen/test_data/rust_parser_fixture.fltkg, which the root Bazel targets
// and the cargo fixture crates build against.
//
// One labeled child, so the generated label accessor (child_value) is reachable
// from both the Python and the Rust generated artifacts.

num := value:/[0-9]+/ ;
